<a href="/articles/14519.html" class="com-grid-banner-article large" >
	<div class="grid-banner-article-hd">
		<div class="imgcover">
				<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/14519/relatedLongPc2/14519.png?1441514958" alt="无印良品在东京开了全球最大旗舰店，拿一万本书做装饰">
		</div>

		<p class="category">
				<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/17/medium/17.png?1411569501" alt="设计">
				<span>设计</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-banner-article-bd clearfix">
		<div class="title-ribbon">
			<h1>无印良品在东京开了全球最大旗舰店，拿一万本书做装饰</h1>
			<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-06 12:59:59 +0800"></span>
			<div class="ribbon">
					<span class="iconfont icon-message">4</span>
					<span class="iconfont icon-heart">125</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>
